FAQ

Q. What is conky-forever?
A. Its just a simple collection of conky configuration and scripts.

Q. Can I modify the conky-forever scripts?
A. Yes, sure you can.

Q. Why are the Fonts preloaded?
A. I don't own those fonts.

Q. Why my distro logo is not shown?
A. I don't use all the distro's, i became too lazy.

Q. Why my clock is not working?
A. clock requries the conky-lua package.

Q. Why does it detect anything other than rhythmbox?
A. I use rhythmbox, you are most welcome to build one your yourself.
